{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b5ac4026ac","title":"福尔克曼《自然科学的认识论原理》一书札记","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bcf6e71083","index":0,"year":1915,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"b5ac4026ac"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","name":"哲学笔记（人民出版社1974年版）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"列宁，人民出版社1974年版","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"b353e6fb43","name":"列宁"}]},"publication_details":{"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"62943954c6","type":"paragraph","text":"保尔·福尔克曼","index":0,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"f2e8576866","type":"paragraph","text":"《自然科学的认识论原理》（《科学和假说》丛书之九）1241910年，莱比锡第2版","index":1,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"e03f35743e","type":"paragraph","text":"（Nat.IV.171，伯尔尼图书馆）①","index":2,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"71623ae446","type":"paragraph","text":"作者在哲学上是个折夷主义者和唐人，特别是在他反对海克尔、谈论布克尔等人的时候。但他毕竟是有唯物主义倾尚的，例如他在第35页②[40③上写道：“有一个问题：是我们把概念加之于自然界，还是自然界把概念加之于我们”—把这两种观点结合起来。马赫是正确的（第38页[43]），但我却以“客观的”观点来同它（马赫的观点）对立。","index":3,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"38f0a462a3","type":"paragraph","text":"“因此我认为：我们的逻辑是以我们之外的事物的规律性进程为基本出发点的；自然过程的外部必然性是我们的第一个导师，而且是最真实的导师。（第39页[437）","index":4,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"aae00440d2","type":"paragraph","text":"作者反对现象学和现代一元论，但他完全不了解唯物主义哲学和唯心主义哲学的实质。其实，他本着一般实证论的精神把问①这是图书编号。译者注B指保尔·福尔克亚《自然科学的认识论原理》（P.Volkmann，Erkenntnis-","index":5,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"3d858c8bd3","type":"paragraph","text":"theoretischeGrundziigederNaturwissenschaften）1910年莱比锡一柏林","index":6,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"baca98be8c","type":"paragraph","text":"德文版的页码。编者注3指保尔·福尔克曼《自然科学的认识论原理》1911年圣被得堡俄文版的页","index":7,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"0d2d7a789f","type":"paragraph","text":"码。→编者注题归结为自然科学的“方法”。他甚至不能提出人类意识（和感觉）之外的自然界的客观实在性问题。","index":8,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"},{"id":"8cdff1b8ec","type":"paragraph","text":"写于1915年1930年第一次载于《列宁文集》第12卷按手稿刊印","index":9,"publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac"}],"page":{"id":"78b0b5021b","publicationId":"0aade93c-c356-46d2-9807-b567596b7e45","articleId":"b5ac4026ac","start":379,"end":380}}}},"__N_SSG":true}